    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-lead-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 assessment plan. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate sufficient credibility to support regulatory decision-making for worst-case operating condition identification in the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. Mean hemolysis index prediction error of 8.4% is within acceptable bounds for the intended regulatory use. Assessment team unanimously recommends acceptance.",
